descript.abstract: Every roadway in El Paso County has a street address range assigned to each side of the street. The street address map can be used to map either single or multiple street address locations. The street Centerline can be used to map the location of an address when typed into the computer, or read a list of addresses from a file and display their many locations.
descript.purpose: The street centerline could be used to direct either a transit vehicle or emergency response vehicle to a given address. It could also be used to map the location of clients, public meeting participants, or any address database.

report.measDesc: No topology has been applied to the layer, yet some QA/QC measures have been applied including checking for: range overlaps with connecting segments, TO address is less than FROM address, segment drawn in the incorrect direction, segments with incorrect jurisdiction, segment name, unsnapped segments, and odd/even parity.
All attributes maintained by addressing are expected to be highly accurate due to QA/Qc procedures, field checks, customer and staff input, and constant maintenance.
